<![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 12pt;">Dear&nbsp;
<span style="font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">{!Order__c.First_Name__c}</span>, <br><br>Thank you&nbsp;for using TrueCost&nbsp;to&nbsp;select and enroll in&nbsp;your current electric plan. &nbsp;We believe that no customer should let their plan expire and revert to potentially higher month-to-month rates because they did not know their current plan would soon expire. </p>
<p style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>According to our records*, your contract at <i>{!Order__c.Service_Address__c}</i> with&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: medium; ">{!Order__c.REP_Profile__c}</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">&nbsp;will expire on or around {!Order__c.Plan_Expiration__c}**, and we'll remind you one more time, <b>5 days</b> before that date.</span></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; "><br></span></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">*</span><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">The Public Utility Commission of Texas also requires that all Retail Electric Providers notify their customers 14 days before a fixed-rate electric plan under contract with their company is about to expire.</span></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">**Your contract expiration date is set by the precise completion date of your enrollment transaction. The estimation shown on&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.mytruecost.com/shopplans" style="font-size: x-small;">myTrueCost.com</a><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;is based on date the Retailer's acceptance date within our portal. Please always verify your contract expiration date on your monthly bill or directly with your Retailer. <b>Tip:</b> Market rules allow you to switch up to 14 days prior to the actual expiration date, without having to specify the contract end date <i>-and- without any penalty</i>.</span></p><p><font size="1"><br></font><font size="3">We can help you find the best electric plan to meet your needs, whether you stay with your current retail electric provider or try a new one.&nbsp; Best of all, your account information is securely stored in our database, so we can place your next order quickly and easily --</font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;">no forms to fill out!</span><br><br><font size="3" style="font-size: 12pt;"><a style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold" href="http://mytruecost.com">Click here to get started</a></font><br><br><font size="3">We look forward to serving you again soon.</font><br><br><br><font size="3">Thank you,</font><br><br><font size="3">TrueCost Customer Support</font></p>
<p style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="mailto:TrueCost@CenterPointEnergy.com">TrueCost@CenterPointEnergy.com</a></p>
